# AGPLv3 License

This project is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3 (AGPLv3).

The AGPLv3 is a free software license that requires:
- Source code to be made available
- Derivative works to use the same license
- Network distribution to include source offer

For full license text, see: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

## Key Points

✅ **You can:**
- Use commercially
- Modify the source code
- Distribute the software
- Patent use of contributions

⚠️ **You must:**
- Include the license
- State significant changes
- Include source code
- Disclose source on network use

❌ **You cannot:**
- Hold liable the authors
- Use trademark
- Apply additional restrictions

